<title>Julius Penson Williams, African American Composer & Conductor</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="African American composer, African American conductor, Videmus Recording Company">
<meta name="description" content="Julius Penson Williams is an African American composer, conductor and professor who was born in the Bronx in 1954. He has been on the faculty of several colleges and universities, and is a co-director of the Videmus Recording Company. As a composer, Williams has written symphonies, dance, musical theater, opera and movies.">
