			<font size="2" face="Verdana">Albany Records Troy 104 (1993)<b>;
			</b><i>Symphonic Brotherhood: The Music of African-American Composers</i>; Everett McCorvey, tenor Bohuslav Martinu Philharmonic; Julius Williams, 
			conductor<b><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; a <a href="Troy104WilliamsIsItTrue.mp3">Is It 
			True?</a><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; b <a href="Troy104MeditationFromTheEasterCelebration.mp3">Meditation 
